  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Spontaneous bacterial peritonitis (SBP) is an ascitic fluid infection in cirrhotic patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Platelet indices can be utilized as a non-invasive predictor of SBP.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
